<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:12:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市因全球科技股上涨而反弹，日元本周下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-19/</link><description>受区域芯片制造商上涨的提振，亚洲股市周五反弹，而日元预计本周将大幅下跌，因为投资者减少了对日本央行将很快放弃超级宽松政策的押注。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:08:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>油价因中国需求担忧而走低</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-drift-lower-china-demand-worries-2024-01-19/</link><description>继前一天上涨后，周五油价下跌，原因是地缘政治紧张局势和冷风造成的美国石油生产中断，以及对中国需求增长缓慢的担忧抵消了这一影响。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-drift-lower-china-demand-worries-2024-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>红海航运袭击给中国出口商造成延误、成本上升的压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/red-sea-crisis-pressures-chinas-exporters-shipping-delays-costs-mount-2024-01-19/</link><description>对于中国商人韩昌明来说，红海货运中断正威胁着他位于东部福建省的贸易公司的生存。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 02:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/red-sea-crisis-pressures-chinas-exporters-shipping-delays-costs-mount-2024-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>麦克吉弗：中国正在迈向毛泽东时代的增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-flirts-with-mao-era-growth-mcgeever-2024-01-19/</link><description>关于中国经济和人口趋势的最新数据引人注目，突显了未来巨大的长期挑战，并将世界第二大经济体的增长状况拖回了 20 世纪 70 年代的孤立时期。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 01:48:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-flirts-with-mao-era-growth-mcgeever-2024-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易代表办公室副代表比安奇将卸任亚洲最高贸易官员职务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/ustr-deputy-bianchi-depart-top-trade-official-asia-2024-01-19/</link><description>白宫周四证实，拜登政府负责亚洲事务的最高贸易官员莎拉·比安奇 (Sarah Bianchi) 即将辞职，美国贸易代表办公室在 11 月份未能达成协议后，正在规划与印太国家贸易谈判的下一步行动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 00:41:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/ustr-deputy-bianchi-depart-top-trade-official-asia-2024-01-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促与中国讨论切实可行的降低核风险措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-urges-discussions-with-china-practical-nuclear-risk-reduction-steps-2024-01-18/</link><description>一位白宫高级官员周四表示，美国预计不会很快与中国进行正式的核军控谈判，但确实希望看到开始讨论实际的降低风险措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 20:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-urges-discussions-with-china-practical-nuclear-risk-reduction-steps-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>中美财长会议在北京召开</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-chinese-finance-officials-open-meetings-beijing-2024-01-18/</link><description>美国财政部和中国财政部官员周四在北京开始为期两天的会议，讨论两个经济大国之间的金融稳定和资本市场问题，加深了去年恢复的接触。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 16:21:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-chinese-finance-officials-open-meetings-beijing-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>迪拜沙漠精英赛首轮李昊桐四路领先</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/golf/li-haotong-four-way-lead-after-first-round-dubai-desert-classic-2024-01-18/</link><description>周四，在阿联酋高尔夫俱乐部举行的迪拜沙漠精英赛中，前冠军李昊桐在第一轮比赛中打出低于标准杆 5 杆的 67 杆，以四路并列领先。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:45:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/golf/li-haotong-four-way-lead-after-first-round-dubai-desert-classic-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>巴西卢拉将于周五会见中国外交部长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/brazils-lula-meet-chinese-foreign-minister-friday-2024-01-18/</link><description>巴西总统发言人周四表示，巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦将于周五下午在巴西东北部城市福塔雷萨会见来访的中国外交部长王毅。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:36:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/brazils-lula-meet-chinese-foreign-minister-friday-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>印度NMDC表示没有计划向中国出口铁矿石</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-nmdc-says-it-has-no-plans-export-iron-ore-china-2024-01-18/</link><description>印度最大的国有铁矿石生产商NMDC Ltd周四表示，没有计划向中国出售铁矿石，正在扩大产量以满足国内需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 15:26:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-nmdc-says-it-has-no-plans-export-iron-ore-china-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>随着新的进口和种植批准，中国对转基因作物的接受势头增强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-embrace-gmo-crops-gains-momentum-with-new-import-planting-approvals-2024-01-18/</link><description>中国周四批准进口和生产更多转基因大豆和玉米品种，同时扩大全国种植面积，作为改善粮食安全和减少进口的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 13:46:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-embrace-gmo-crops-gains-momentum-with-new-import-planting-approvals-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国通过丝绸之路大型港口拓宽南美贸易高速公路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-widens-south-america-trade-highway-with-silk-road-mega-port-2024-01-18/</link><description>一个中国大型港口正在太平洋沿岸崛起，有望增强与南美的贸易关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 11:06:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-widens-south-america-trade-highway-with-silk-road-mega-port-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>沉阳文件未讨论出售中国宝马合资公司股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/no-discussion-sale-stake-china-bmw-joint-venture-shenyang-document-2024-01-18/</link><description>路透社周四看到的一份文件显示，宝马在中国的合作伙伴没有计划出售其合资企业的股份，这与本周早些时候的媒体报道相矛盾。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 10:39:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/no-discussion-sale-stake-china-bmw-joint-venture-shenyang-document-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>LME首席执行官计划于2024年与上海期货交易所签订第一批合约</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-ceo-aims-have-first-contracts-with-shanghai-futures-exchange-2024-2024-01-18/</link><description>伦敦金属交易所（LME）首席执行官在世界经济论坛（WEF）年会间隙告诉路透社，伦敦金属交易所（LME）计划今年试点使用上海期货交易所（ShFE）价格的合约。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 09:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-ceo-aims-have-first-contracts-with-shanghai-futures-exchange-2024-2024-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：如果边境保持平静，印度可能放松对中国的投资限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-could-ease-china-investment-curbs-if-border-stays-calm-2024-01-18/</link><description>印度一名高级官员表示，如果两国边境保持和平，印度可能会放松对中国投资的严格审查，这是印度可能取消长达四年的限制的首个信号。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 08:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-could-ease-china-investment-curbs-if-border-stays-calm-2024-01-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>